---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Cookie Policy — Fatima Saleh" description="How this site uses cookies and browser storage.">
  <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 py-16 sm:py-24">
    <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-semibold mb-2">Cookie Policy</h1>
    <p class="text-muted text-sm mb-10">Last updated: March 2025</p>

    <div class="prose prose-neutral max-w-none space-y-8 text-ink/90 leading-relaxed">

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">1. What are cookies?</h2>
        <p>
          Cookies are small text files that websites store on your device. They are widely used to make sites
          work efficiently, remember your preferences, and provide information to website owners.
          <code class="bg-cream/60 px-1 rounded text-sm">localStorage</code> is a similar browser-based
          storage mechanism that persists data locally without sending it to a server on each request.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">2. How this site uses cookies and local storage</h2>
        <p>
          This site uses <strong>no tracking cookies</strong> and <strong>no third-party analytics cookies</strong>.
          We do not use Google Analytics, Facebook Pixel, or any other advertising or tracking technology.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-3">
          The only browser storage this site sets is a single <code class="bg-cream/60 px-1 rounded text-sm">localStorage</code>
          key used to remember your cookie consent preference:
        </p>
        <table class="w-full mt-4 text-sm border-collapse">
          <thead>
            <tr class="border-b border-ink/20">
              <th class="text-left py-2 pr-4 font-semibold">Key</th>
              <th class="text-left py-2 pr-4 font-semibold">Type</th>
              <th class="text-left py-2 font-semibold">Purpose</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody>
            <tr class="border-b border-ink/10">
              <td class="py-2 pr-4"><code class="bg-cream/60 px-1 rounded">cookie_consent</code></td>
              <td class="py-2 pr-4">localStorage (functional)</td>
              <td class="py-2">Remembers whether you have accepted or dismissed the cookie notice, so it is not shown again on return visits.</td>
            </tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
        <p class="mt-4">
          This key is stored locally in your browser only. It is never sent to our servers or shared with any third party.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">3. No third-party cookies</h2>
        <p>
          We do not embed any third-party widgets, social sharing buttons, or advertising scripts that would
          set cookies on your device. If this changes in the future, this policy will be updated accordingly.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">4. How to manage or delete cookies</h2>
        <p>
          You can clear localStorage at any time through your browser's developer tools or privacy settings.
          The steps vary by browser:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mt-2 space-y-1">
          <li><strong>Chrome:</strong> Settings → Privacy and security → Clear browsing data</li>
          <li><strong>Firefox:</strong> Settings → Privacy &amp; Security → Cookies and Site Data → Clear Data</li>
          <li><strong>Safari:</strong> Preferences → Privacy → Manage Website Data</li>
          <li><strong>Edge:</strong> Settings → Privacy, search, and services → Clear browsing data</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-3">
          Clearing this data will reset your cookie consent preference and the notice will appear again on your
          next visit.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">5. Changes to this policy</h2>
        <p>
          If we begin using additional cookies or storage mechanisms in the future, this policy will be updated
          before those changes go live. The date at the top of this page indicates the last revision.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">6. Contact</h2>
        <p>
          Questions about cookies or data storage? Contact:<br />
          <strong>Fatima Saleh</strong><br />
          <a href="mailto:hello@fatimasaleh.com" class="underline hover:text-burgundy transition-colors">hello@fatimasaleh.com</a>
        </p>
        <p class="mt-3">
          For broader data privacy information, see the <a href="/privacy-policy" class="underline hover:text-burgundy transition-colors">Privacy Policy</a>.
        </p>
      </section>

    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
